cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on natural language generation and transfer learning, which are both core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks for text generation, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) in the form of using external textual sources to ground the generated text. Finally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which are often associated with neural networks and can fall under the category of neural engineering (cs.NE).
